#new:String $PriestSpeech
{
[Style Right]
[Shake]Gahahahahaaa![/fx][BR]
[Pause 10]You don't get it, do you?[BR]
You're too stupid to realize what[BR]
it is you've done...[BR]
[Wait][Next]
The [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Deities[RestoreColor] were the ones[BR]
holding the seals to [SaveColor][Color:07]The Almighty[RestoreColor].[BR]
[Pause 10]In freeing them, you've only served[BR]
the purpose of assisting me![BR]
[Wait][Next]
We're mere moments from witnessing[BR]
[SaveColor][Color:07]Our Overlord[RestoreColor]'s rebirth![BR]
[Pause 5][SizeWave]An overjoyed feeling...[/fx][BR]
[Wait][Next]
[Size 48][Pause 8][Shake][InputOff][Speed delay=4 chars=1]Awaken!!![BR]
[Pause 60][End]
}

#new:String $PriestSpeech2
