[PrintRising]At last! [Shake]At long last![/fx][/fx][BR]
[Pause 15][SaveColor][Color:07]Our Overlord[RestoreColor] is finally going to[BR]
grant us his panacea![BR]
[Wait][Next]
[PrintRising]We're all ascending![BR]
[Pause 12]Honey, I'm coming home![/fx][BR]
[Pause 5][SizeJitter][Size 24]Gaaahahahahaaaa![/fx]
[Wait][End]
}

